<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.1">
<l>vaṅkamā munnīr variniṟap periya vāḷara viṉaṇai mēvi</l>
<l>caṅkamā raṅkait taṭamala runtic cāmamā mēṉiyeṉ talaivaṉ</l>
<l>aṅkamā ṟaintu vēḷvināl vēta maruṅkalai payiṉṟeri mūṉṟum</l>
<l>ceṅkaiyāl vaḷarkkum tuḷakkamil maṉattōr tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My lord with a great dark body, navel with a broad flower,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] a lovely hand with a conch,</l>
<l>Abiding in the great, wavy three-watered [sea] on a bed</l>
<l rend="indent">[that is] a huge, radiant serpent of varied color,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi with those whose minds never waver,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, practicing the rare arts</l>
<l>Of the six branches [of knowledge], the five sacrifices, and the four Vedas,</l>
<l rend="indent">tend the three fires with fine hands.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
